{
  "stem": "1753.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 15.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You go there, and-- and the-- the-- the truck always stops there at the Pawiak prison, the famous Pawiak prison.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And so I went there, and then never returned.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And when I got back, I found out that my father had perished, that he died.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So that was quite bad.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I used to send things that-- you were able to-- to get-- send packages there, but probably never got to him.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I-- and he just perished.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think he starved to death, or something like that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went back into the ghetto, but there was no future there either.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A couple days later, I went-- again.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I heard of another camp, which was on the other side, near Warszawa Praga, a sizable project where they were building a fuel depot for their eventual plans to attack-- attack Russia.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, that was in 1941.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was in 1941.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there were-- there were about 3,000 Jewish workers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And a few years ago, I-- coincidentally, I met a Jewish man here in LA that also worked there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But he was pretending he was a-- a-- a-- an Aryan, a Pole.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He speaks perfect Polish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he worked there too, but not as a Jew.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They could go home every night, but we had to go in a camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That camp was fair.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Nothing was-- it was no resort, I guarantee you, but it was fair.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they gave you halfway decent food.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In fact, you got paid.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The first few months, they paid everybody.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was something very, very unusual.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "In the Polish zloty, they paid you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And you got paid every week, until one Friday they said here.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they-- they-- they say here.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
